这位歌手的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-revealed-devastating-impact-of-sons-death-in-final-social-media-post-3474211">最后一篇社交媒体帖子揭示了她儿子去年去世的毁灭性影响</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sinead-oconnor-fans-gather-to-sing-nothing-compares-2-u-at-dublin-tribute-3475498">观看 Sinéad O&#39;Connor 歌迷聚集在都柏林致敬歌曲《Nothing Compares 2 U》的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
